OL,3,CWoman falsely accused of harming
OL,4,Cseagull in viral video speaks out
OL,6,FA Muslim woman who was subjected to a
OL,7,Fstream of Islamophobic abuse after a
OL,8,Fvideo of her rescuing a seagull went
OL,9,Fviral online says racists should not
OL,10,Fbe allowed to "divide us".
OL,12,FNora Mubarak was falsely accused of
OL,13,Ftrying to harm the bird after footage
OL,14,Fshared by a number of high-profile
OL,15,Fright wing social media accounts
OL,16,Fgained millions of views.
OL,18,FThe video prompted thousands of racist
OL,19,Fcomments, many peddling fake claims
OL,20,Fshe intended to eat the animal.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
