OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783945155
OL,3,CWoman falsely accused of harming
OL,4,Cseagull in viral video speaks out
OL,6,FCllr Oliver Freeston, Reform leader of
OL,7,FNorth East Lincolnshire Council, was
OL,8,Famong those forced to issue a
OL,9,Fretraction after he implied the
OL,10,Fseagull was at risk.
OL,12,FMs Mubarak, who is from the Middle
OL,13,FEast but has legal status in the UK
OL,14,Fand is a self-confessed bird lover,
OL,15,Fsaid: "I found out these lies are
OL,16,Fbeing spread around me, which was
OL,17,Fdiscouraging.
OL,19,F"They have an agenda to divide us, and
OL,20,Fwe should not let them do so."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
