FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783945155
OL,3,CWoman falsely accused of harming
OL,4,Cseagull in viral video speaks out
OL,6,FThe initial video showed Ms Mubarak
OL,7,Fusing a sheet to capture the young
OL,8,Fbird after seeing it lying injured on
OL,9,Fa street in Grimsby.
OL,11,FShe then enlisted the help of a local
OL,12,Fcarpet shop to return it to the roof
OL,13,Fwhere its mother was nesting.
OL,15,FMs Mubarak posted a second video on
OL,16,Fthe Seagull Appreciation Society
OL,17,FFacebook page showing the gull being
OL,18,Freturned to its mother, with a message
OL,19,Fthat "goodness and kindness still
OL,20,Fexist".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783945155
OL,3,CWoman falsely accused of harming
OL,4,Cseagull in viral video speaks out
OL,6,FBut after being targeted over the
OL,7,Finitial footage, she said she was now
OL,8,Fhaving to wear a face mask to protect
OL,9,Fher identity.
OL,11,FAmong those who shared the video was
OL,12,FCllr Freeston, who wrote: "Grimsby in
OL,13,F2026. I would remind all that in the
OL,14,FUK, all wild gulls are protected by
OL,15,Fthe Wildlife and Countryside Act 1981.
OL,16,FPerhaps Nigel Farage was right..."
OL,18,FHe later deleted the post, admitting
OL,19,Fhe had misrepresented what it showed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
