PN,33405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783945155
OL,3,CWoman falsely accused of harming
OL,4,Cseagull in viral video speaks out
OL,6,FHe said: "Really pleased it's now
OL,7,Fconfirmed that the lady in the video
OL,8,Fwas actually rescuing the seagull."
OL,10,F"The video was very distressing for
OL,11,Fall to watch as we are a nation of
OL,12,Fanimal lovers. Credit where credit is
OL,13,Fdue, fair play to the lady for
OL,14,Frescuing the bird."
OL,16,FHe also offered to make a donation to
OL,17,Fan animal charity.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
