FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783945155
OL,3,CWoman falsely accused of harming
OL,4,Cseagull in viral video speaks out
OL,6,FBut Ms Mubarak said: "I don't need his
OL,7,Fdonation. I don't need (his apologies)
OL,8,F- it's not accepted because he lied
OL,9,Fabout me. He lied to the people, and
OL,10,Fhe should be responsible for that."
OL,12,FMelanie Ann, Labour MP for Great
OL,13,FGrimsby and Cleethorpes criticised
OL,14,FCllr Freeston over his original post,
OL,15,Fand said: "If you're in a position of
OL,16,Fleadership in a local community you
OL,17,Fhave a duty of due diligence and its
OL,18,Freally important to fact check."
OL,26,@oD@XpmoD@fpnwD@KOUzD@`O]
